Privacy PolicyWe care about your data...

  1. We're storing your settings and uploads.

  2. By logging in to dashboard you agree to join our support server.

  3. Deleting/wiping your images is irreversible.

  4. You can request account deletion by creating ticket in our support server.

  5. You can't delete anything from hastebin.
